Noncommercial Purposes

Noncommercial purposes are purposes other than gaining a financial benefit, directly or indirectly. "Financial benefit" includes receiving money, credits toward a purchase, or other forms of compensation.

Acceptance and Conditions

To receive this license, you must agree to its rules. The rules of this license are both obligations under that agreement and conditions to your license. You must not do anything with the software that triggers a rule that you cannot or will not follow.

